                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-231-off1233 t18311201-231-crimeloc1235"></join>; the lad went into Neal's shop, took the bacon off the counter, and gave it to the prisoner in the passage - they both ran away; I followed, and took the prisoner with it under his arm.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-231-person1791">
                  MARY 
                  NEAL
               <interp inst="t18311201-231-person1791" type="surname" value="NEAL"></interp>
