                     <interp inst="t18311201-231-person1791" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the wife of Patrick Neal, of John's-row. I heard the scales rattle in the shop, I ran out, and the bacon was gone; the Policeman brought the prisoner in with it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was not in the passage; a boy betrayed me from work, and put the bacon into my arms.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
